[I] Contact Manager

[T] KAddressBook stores all the personal details of your family, friends and
[T] other contacts. It supports large variety of services, including NextCloud,
[T] Kolab, Google Contacts, Microsoft Exchange (EWS) or any standard CalDAV
[T] server.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kaddressbook/

